<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body class="bg-slate-600">
    <header class="bg-blue-500 text-white py-6">
        <h1 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold">About Us</h1>
    </header>

    <main class="container mx-auto my-10 px-5">
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-400 mb-4">Who We Are</h2>
            <p class="text-white leading-loose">
                We are a leading company dedicated to providing top-notch services to our clients. Our mission is to
                deliver quality solutions while ensuring customer satisfaction. With years of experience in the industry,
                we are proud to have built a reputation for reliability and excellence.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-400 mb-4">Our Vision</h2>
            <p class="text-white leading-loose">
                Our vision is to continuously innovate and grow, making a significant impact in our industry. We aim to
                empower businesses with our expertise and help them achieve their goals.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-400 mb-4">Why Choose Us</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white leading-loose">
                <li>Experienced professionals</li>
                <li>Customer-centric approach</li>
                <li>High-quality solutions</li>
                <li>Commitment to excellence</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>


    
    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-gray-300 py-10">
        <div class="container mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- About Section -->
            <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">About Us</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">
                    Welcome to our website! We are committed to delivering high-quality services to our customers. Stay connected for updates and support.
                </p>
            </div>
    
            <!-- Links Section -->
            <div class="text-center">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Quick Links</h3>
                <ul class="text-sm space-y-2">
                    <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-blue-400">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about" class="hover:text-blue-400">About Us</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:text-blue-400">Contact Us</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-blue-400">Services</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
    
            <!-- Contact Section -->
            <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Contact Us</h3>
                <ul class="text-sm">
                    <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@example.com" class="hover:text-blue-400">support@example.com</a></li>
                    <li>Phone: <a href="tel:+123456789" class="hover:text-blue-400">+1 234 567 89</a></li>
                    <li>Address: 123, Main Street, City, Country</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <div class="mt-8 border-t border-gray-700 pt-5 text-center text-sm">
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your Company Name. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>

</html>
